---

### PromptBuilder Upgrades (3 layers)

#### [MODIFY] [promptBuilder.js](file:///e:/StoryForge/src/services/ai/promptBuilder.js)

**Layer 3 — Genre:** Ưu tiên `project.ai_guidelines` nếu có, fallback về `GENRE_CONSTRAINTS[genre]` nếu không. Tone adjustments theo `ai_strictness`.

```diff
-  const genreConstraint = GENRE_CONSTRAINTS[genreKey];
-  if (genreConstraint) {
-    systemParts.push(`\n[THỂ LOẠI]\n${genreConstraint}`);
-  }
+  // Ưu tiên ai_guidelines (editable), fallback genre constraint
+  if (aiGuidelines) {
+    systemParts.push(`\n[CHỈ DẪN TÁC GIẢ]\n${aiGuidelines}`);
+  } else if (genreConstraint) {
+    systemParts.push(`\n[THỂ LOẠI]\n${genreConstraint}`);
+  }
```

**Layer 5 — Characters:** Inject relationships nếu có.

```javascript
// Sau khi inject characters, thêm:
if (relationships.length > 0) {
  const relInfo = relationships.map(r => 
    `- ${r.charA} ⟷ ${r.charB}: ${r.label}${r.description ? ` (${r.description})` : ''}`
  ).join('\n');
  systemParts.push(`\n[QUAN HỆ NHÂN VẬT]\n${relInfo}`);
}
```

**Layer 6 — Scene Contract (MỚI):** Inject khi có data.

```javascript
// Layer 6: Scene Contract — chỉ inject fields có data
const contractParts = [];
if (sceneContract.goal) contractParts.push(`Mục tiêu: ${sceneContract.goal}`);
if (sceneContract.conflict) contractParts.push(`Xung đột: ${sceneContract.conflict}`);
if (sceneContract.emotional_start || sceneContract.emotional_end)
  contractParts.push(`Cảm xúc: ${sceneContract.emotional_start} → ${sceneContract.emotional_end}`);
if (sceneContract.must_happen?.length)
  contractParts.push(`BẮT BUỘC:\n${sceneContract.must_happen.map(m=>`✅ ${m}`).join('\n')}`);
if (sceneContract.must_not_happen?.length)
  contractParts.push(`CẤM:\n${sceneContract.must_not_happen.map(m=>`⛔ ${m}`).join('\n')}`);
if (sceneContract.pacing) contractParts.push(`Nhịp: ${sceneContract.pacing}`);
// Tone adjustment theo ai_strictness
if (contractParts.length > 0) {
  const prefix = strictness === 'strict' ? 'BẮT BUỘC tuân thủ' : 
                 strictness === 'relaxed' ? 'Tham khảo' : 'Tuân theo';
  systemParts.push(`\n[HỢP ĐỒNG CẢNH — ${prefix}]\n${contractParts.join('\n')}`);
}
```

**Taboos tone** theo `ai_strictness`:

```diff
-  tabooLines = `⛔ TUYỆT ĐỐI KHÔNG: ${who} — ${t.description}`;
+  const tabooPrefix = strictness === 'strict' ? '⛔ TUYỆT ĐỐI KHÔNG' :
+                      strictness === 'relaxed' ? '⚠️ Nên tránh' : '❌ Không nên';
```

