### Context Engine Updates

#### [MODIFY] [contextEngine.js](file:///e:/StoryForge/src/services/ai/contextEngine.js)

1. **Fix entity detection** — `includes()` → word boundary regex
2. **Load relationships** cho detected characters
3. **Load scene contract data** (existing + new fields)
4. **Truyền `ai_guidelines`, `ai_strictness`** từ project

```diff
-  const detectedCharacters = allCharacters.filter(
-    c => c.name && cleanText.includes(c.name.toLowerCase())
-  );
+  const detectedCharacters = allCharacters.filter(c => {
+    if (!c.name || c.name.length < 2) return false;
+    const regex = new RegExp(`\\b${escapeRegex(c.name)}\\b`, 'i');
+    return regex.test(cleanText);
+  });
```

